CRC cluster {{ crc_cluster_name }}

DNS server for WireGuard clients: {{ crc_bind_address }}

Canonical CRC names:
  API:     https://api.crc.testing:6443
  Console: https://console-openshift-console.apps-crc.testing

Cluster-scoped names exposed by HAProxy/dnsmasq:
  API:     https://{{ crc_api_alias }}:6443
  Console: https://{{ crc_console_alias }}
  OAuth:   https://{{ crc_oauth_alias }}

Custom domains managed by the playbook:
  API domain:  {{ crc_api_domain }}
  Apps domain: {{ crc_apps_domain }}

The playbook configures ingress appsDomain/componentRoutes and API named
certificates when crc_configure_custom_domains is enabled.

Get credentials on the host:
  crc console --credentials
